排放汇总于表6。</p><p>用于胶结料的水泥、石灰、乳化沥青等都是高耗能材料。运输能耗在新集料能耗中占较大比重，为</p><table-wrap id="table3" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table3">Table 3</xref></label><caption><title> Explosives amounts and quantity of limestone aggregate exploitatio</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >工作日</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >石料开采量(t)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >炸药用量(kg)</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5400</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >810</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5500</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >805</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5400</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >806</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5100</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >813</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >6000</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >817</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >6</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5550</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >811</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表3. 炸药用量及石灰岩开采量调查表</p><table-wrap id="table4" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table4">Table 4</xref></label><caption><title> Daily output and energy consumption of crushers (limestone</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >工作日</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >连续工作时间(h)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >产量(t)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >耗电量(kwh)</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >12</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5040</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4800</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle